---
import Base from '@baselayout';
---

<Base title="About">
	<h2
		class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-wide text-accentColor w500:text-lg"
	>
		<a
			href="/"
			class="underline transition-colors hover:text-lightModeText dark:hover:text-darkModeText"
			>~</a
		>/<a
			href="/portfolio"
			class="underline transition-colors hover:text-lightModeText dark:hover:text-darkModeText"
			>portfolio</a
		>/synthetic-biology
	</h2>

	<div
		class="prose mt-4 text-left tracking-wide text-lightModeText prose-code:rounded-sm prose-code:bg-lightCodeBg prose-code:px-1 prose-code:py-0.5 prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none dark:text-darkModeText prose-code:dark:bg-darkCodeBg w500:text-sm w500:leading-[2.2]"
	>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Synthetic Biology is the way forward into the future of
			biotechnology. It is an interdisciplinary field that combines
			biology, engineering, and computer science to design and construct
			new biological systems. I have always been fascinated by the
			potential of synthetic biology, and aim to contribute to its
			foundational advance as a career.
		</p>
		<p class="mb-4">
			If you are interested, I am happy to share my portfolio projects
			with you. You may view or download them below.
		</p>
		<h2 class="mb-2 text-accentColor">Documents</h2>
		<ol class="text-white">
			<li>
				<a
					class="underline transition-colors hover:!text-accentColor dark:text-darkModeText w500:text-sm"
					href="/portfolio/synthetic-biology/trev-fox_m1-scientific-project.pdf"
					>M1 Internship Scientific Project</a
				><i class="ri-file-pdf-2-fill ri-lg ml-1 text-red-400"></i>
				<ol class="mt-0">
					The M1 Scientific Project is an assignment that describes
					what work will be done during the M1 Internship. My M1
					internship is with the Genoscope laboratory, in
					collaboration with the iGEM team "Evry_Paris-Saclay".
				</ol>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a href="https://2022.igem.wiki/ubc-okanagan" target="_blank"
					>2022 iGEM Project Wiki - Life Bulb</a
				><i class="ri-external-link-fill ri-lg ml-1"></i>
			</li>
		</ol>
	</div>
</Base>

<style>
	ol li a {
		@apply underline decoration-accentColor decoration-2 transition-colors hover:!text-accentColor dark:text-darkModeText w500:text-sm;
	}
</style>
